Package: segra
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Segergren <olle.segergren@gmail.com>
Section: video
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://segra.tv
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, gstreamer1.0-libav, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, ffmpeg, pipewire, wireplumber, xdg-desktop-portal, xdg-desktop-portal-gtk, zenity, pulseaudio-utils
Recommends: libgdiplus, x11-xserver-utils, xclip
Description: Segra game clip recorder
 Segra records your gameplay and lets you clip and share it. The recorder
 (OBS/libobs) is downloaded automatically on first launch, so the package
 itself stays small.
